title: Top 15 Offensive Prospects of the NFL Draft, Gronk's Future and Dez's Destination | GM Street (Ep. 256)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier kick off NFL draft week by discussing Rob Gronkowski's comments regarding his future in football (03:45) and where Dez Bryant could end up (06:15). Then they dive into their top 15 draft prospects on the offensive side of the ball (22:15).
